@Date:	29-JUL-1964
@Situation:	Although this recording was made one week after the preceeding one , the two are given the same number , 39 , because noise masked all but the first 6 minutes of the previous recording made at Revere Beach. Ellen Goldman , another research assistant at the Cognitive Center Annex , accompanied Courtney. Although the hum level is high , Sarah's voice is quite clear
